%p
  This app is meant to help technical writers find content that needs
  periodic review and flag it as such. It's also maybe a helpful tool
  for inventorying content and learning things about our content. 

- unless user_signed_in? == false
  %h3 Pages by Projects
  - projects = {"pe" => [3.3,3.7], "puppet" => [3.6, 3.7], "hiera" => [1]}
  %ul
    - projects.each do |project, versions|
      %li
        %h4= project
        %ul
          - versions.each do |version|
            %li
              %a{:href => "/pages/#{project}/#{version}"}
                = version

